l=\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"margin:0;border:0;cursor: pointer;\" src=\"//www.moe.gov.cn/images/moe_icon_jiucuo.png?v=bm05000001\" /></a></span>\n      <ul>\n        <li class=\"sm\" id=\"moe_index_foot_sm\"><a href=\"http://www.moe.gov.cn/jyb_sy/s3634/201005/t20100504_87292.html\" target=\"_blank\">网站声明</a></li>\n        <li class=\"dt\" id=\"moe_index_foot_dt\"><a href=\"http://www.moe.gov.cn/jyb_sy/s3636/202404/t20240411_1125026.html\" target=\"_blank\">网站地图</a></li>\n        <li class=\"lx\" id=\"moe_index_foot_lx\"><a href=\"http://www.moe.gov.cn/jyb_sy/s3635/201611/t20161129_290403.html\" target=\"_blank\">联系我们</a></li>\n      </ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"scy-foot-xia\">\n      <p>版权所有：中华人民共和国教育部&nbsp;中文域名：教育部.政务</p>\n      <p><a class=\"outMoeLink\" href=\"https://beian.miit.gov.cn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">京ICP备10028400号-1</a>&nbsp;<a class=\"outMoeLink\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.beian.gov.cn/portal/registerSystemInfo?recordcode=11010202007625\" rel=\"nofollow\" id=\"moe_gonganbeian\">京公网安备11010202007625号</a>&nbsp;<span>网站标识码：bm05000001</span></p>\n</div>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/images/wailian.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/toolbar/esdToolsInit.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"javascript\" async src=\"/mokuai/webdig_moe/webdig_moe.js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" language=\"javascript\" async src=\"/images/tmp.moe.qt.v1.js\"></script>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"m_position_fixed_A pchide\"><div class=\"m_return_top\" id=\"returnTopFun\"></div></div>\n<div id=\"app_div\" style=\"display:none;\" >\n<form id=\"pdfform\"><input name=\"url\" type=\"hidden\" id=\"url\" /><input name=\"opertime\" type=\"hidden\" id=\"opertime\" value=\"2024-11-13 13:30:48\" /></form>\n</div>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"../../../images/m_index.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>",
